    {
      "image": "assets/images/00.png",
      "en": "Planet Earth and the Solar System",
      "cn": "第 37 篇",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/01.png",
      "en": "We live on the planet Earth.",
      "cn": "我们生活在地球这颗行星上。",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/02.png",
      "en": "Our planet has water and land.",
      "cn": "我们的星球有水和陆地。",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/03.png",
      "en": "In the water, there are lots of amazing fish and sea creatures.",
      "cn": "水里有许多奇妙的鱼和海洋生物。",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/04.png",
      "en": "On land, we build comfortable homes, grow plants and take care of animals.",
      "cn": "在陆地上，我们建造舒适的家，种植植物并照顾动物。",
      "unit": 1
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/05.png",
      "en": "The moon travels around the earth.",
      "cn": "月亮围绕地球运行。",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/06.png",
      "en": "Brave astronauts travel to the moon in a rocket to see what they can find.",
      "cn": "勇敢的宇航员乘火箭去月球，看看他们能发现什么。",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/07.png",
      "en": "Earth is in the solar system.",
      "cn": "地球在太阳系中。",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/08.png",
      "en": "At the central part of our solar system is the sun.",
      "cn": "太阳位于我们太阳系的中心部分。",
      "unit": 2
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/09.png",
      "en": "There are 8 planets in our solar system that all move around the sun in a big circle.",
      "cn": "太阳系中有 8 颗行星，它们都围绕太阳沿一个大圆圈运动。",
      "unit": 3
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/10.png",
      "en": "The planet closest to the sun is Mercury.",
      "cn": "离太阳最近的行星是水星。",
      "unit": 3
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/11.png",
      "en": "As the biggest planet, Jupiter is made of gas.",
      "cn": "作为最大的行星，木星由气体组成。",
      "unit": 3
    },
    {
      "image": "assets/images/12.png",
      "en": "The planet furthest away from the sun is Neptune, feeling quite lonely in the outer reaches.",
      "cn": "离太阳最远的行星是海王星，它在遥远的外层区域显得相当孤独。",
      "unit": 3
    }
  ],
